name: Una anestesia local
description:
This image is part of a series called "Manos" (Hands), created for a daily photography challenge. It was my first conceptual photography project. 

"Una anestesia local" (A local anesthesia), represents how many people who live surrounded by mosquitoes find this technique helpful to relieve -momentarily- itching after a mosquito bite.

For more content, find me on Social Media as @lauridomm
